{"tid":1975555,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【廢老巴菲特】西方石油以股代息　巴菲特都無息收","createTime":"2020-04-16T15:23:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-17T01:53:57.000Z","uid":93980,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"606ef8e91dbb09efc73b5ca12ed87a992f04b68c","tid":1975555,"uid":93980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T15:23:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d9QHTaB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd9QHTaB.png&h=66b4c3bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n國際油價暴跌，美國上周原油庫存增加1900萬桶，創有紀錄以來最大一周升幅。市場預計，全球原油需求將因為新型肺炎疫情打擊跌至25年低位，昨日紐約期油一度跌穿20美元。<br />\n<br />\n美國作為產油成本最貴的產油國之一，美國能源股自然當災。西方石油的現金流更出現壓力。路透社報道，周三（16日）西方石油向監管機構披露，將會以普通股支付原來給巴郡（Berkshire Hathaway）的2億美元的股息。<br />\n<br />\n以周二（14日）收市價14.90美元計算，這筆給巴郡的股票約價值2.57億美元，比原來2億美元股息更高，不過，西方石油現時跌3.27%，報13.159元，以此計算，這筆股票的價值已大縮水至2.2億美元。<br />\n<br />\n目前巴郡持有西方石油4.7%股入以及價值100億美元的優先股。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2619789\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2619789&d=74s%2FNZguDZpTF4W18ni10D%2BzTm40CM4Hl%2BPVqeZuRg0%3D&h=04e01a06\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2619789</a>"},{"pid":"469c817e7e920026114c9da3a7da05f25bc54621","tid":1975555,"uid":93980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T15:29:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0049150269fe5d895e7d7de9c718cd2be4d37a79","tid":1975555,"uid":93980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T15:39:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a0263434bcaa390264006fe56d42223532529c6","tid":1975555,"uid":93980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T15:44:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e8b9cf